{"_path":"/city/t029","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"火災逃生避難流程","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t029-1.jpeg","sequence":29,"category":"火災逃生","author":"消防署","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-06-03T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"火災逃生避難流程"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"火災逃生避難流程"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"【高樓層遇到火災 我們能做什麼？】"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n現代的房子越蓋越高，高樓層集合住宅也越來越多，萬一遇到火災，該如何應變？"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 聽到火災警報"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n火災發生時，首先要大聲叫醒所有家人，一起逃生避難。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 嘗試往下、往外逃生"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n火場逃生最佳策略就是離開建築物，而離開建築物最好的方法就是往一樓往外逃生。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 確認逃生動線上是否有煙"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n火場產生的「煙」既高溫又帶有毒性，是火場的頭號殺手，在逃生時要確認逃生動線上是否有煙，可伸手觸摸門板上方，確認是否很燙，若很燙代表門外有煙，動線不安全，要另擇逃生路線。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 無法逃出，關門就地避難"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n萬一門外有煙，又沒有其他逃生路線，此時最好的方法就是把門關上並利用手邊工具(如毛巾、衣服等)塞住門縫，避免毒煙滲入。\n關門後，開窗求救並保持低姿勢避免吸到毒煙。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 撥打 119 報案"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n保持冷靜，告知門牌幾號？住在幾樓？有多少人員受困？並依照 119 執勤員指示等待救援。\n火場瞬息萬變，逃生機會往往只在一念之間，需以遠離火煙為原則，視現場情況臨機應變。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.tfdp.com.tw/cht/index.php"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"消防防災館"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQMLIpCp-D8"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"火場生存術 完整版-中文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E9BTCC1yX94"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"滅火器操作方式"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"t029-1.jpeg","src":"/images/city/t029-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"火災逃生避難流程","depth":2,"text":"火災逃生避難流程"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:city:t029.md","_source":"content","_file":"city/t029.md","_extension":"md"}